long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Chrome extension for GraphQL Playground using the last Playground version.

Use it to debug or run Queries and Mutations to a GraphQL server directly from your browser.

The latest version of this extension brings the most recent Playground build and also a couple fixes that makes it possible to run again with last chrome version
